      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">The Blessed Path: Why 90% of Agent Success is Documentation You Already Wrote</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">The single biggest predictor of AI agent success is not the model, the prompt, or the framework. It is documentation. The blessed path is where agents thrive. Everything else is a hallucination waiting to happen.</p>
